this.tree = new DialogTree();
this.tree.npcHeader = "Now that you've got your A-280, head on over to the range and blast some targets. Make sure you bring me back at least 5 of your targets so I can see what kind of shot you are.";
this.tree.response1 = "Aye Aye Sir!
";
this.tree.response1DT = new DialogTree();
this.tree.response1DT.npcHeader = "Well you've sure got two eyes and you can see the target, but it looks like you might have learned how to shoot from a Stormtrooper, Shiny.
";
this.tree.response1DT.response1 = "Is it really that bad?
";
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT = new DialogTree();
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT.npcHeader = "It looks worse than a Tauntaun smells, that's for sure.
";
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT.response1 = "What's a Tauntaun?
";
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT.response1DT = new DialogTree();
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT.response1DT.npcHeader = "Enough chatter Shiny, now that you've got your armor and proved you're capable of firing a blaster, it's my duty to welcome you fully into The Rebel Alliance. Take a while and get acquainted with the base and the other Rebels, and don't even think about taking a ship out seeing as how you lack the training. When you're ready for your first assignment come find me. I'll give you a hint where you'll be going, it's cold and there's Wampas.";
this.tree.response1DT.response1DT.response2 = "I eat Tauntaun for breakfast old man.
";
